author: gatfora
msg: For a 2-way sequence, the LastMessage never gets sent for a response sequence if the sequence was setup to use async communications.  This patch changes to send the response sequence to the defined reply to address which had been set on the sequence.  There is a bit of cleanup surrounding Ack processing for terminated sequences and removed several unused imports.
